 🔒 Security
 </h2>
 <div className="bg-surface border-edge rounded-xl border p-8 shadow-[0_1px_3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] transition-shadow hover:shadow-[0_2px_8px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] max-sm:p-6">
